<concept id="id_2" class="- topic/topic concept/concept "><title class="- topic/title ">Chrome</title><conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody "><p class="- topic/p ">To use Katalon Studio with the Incognito mode of Chrome, do as follows:</p><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">In <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Katalon Studio</uicontrol>, go to <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Project &gt; Settings &gt; Desired Capabilities &gt; Web UI &gt; Chrome</b>.</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Click <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Add</b> on the command toolbar, then input the following values:</p><table class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><thead class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry class="- topic/entry ">Name</entry><entry class="- topic/entry ">Type</entry><entry class="- topic/entry ">Value</entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry class="- topic/entry ">args</entry><entry class="- topic/entry ">List</entry><entry class="- topic/entry ">--incognito</entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table><p class="- topic/p "><image width="700" href="image/ks-850-incognito-dc.png" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">setting desired capabilities for Chrome</alt></image><image width="700" href="image/ks-850-incognito.png" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">incognito</alt></image></p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Click <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Apply and Close</b>. You can now execute tests in Incognito mode of Chrome. </p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> To use the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Record and Spy</uicontrol> utility of <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Katalon Studio</uicontrol> in Incognito mode of Chrome, you need to allow the Katalon Studio extension to run in Incognito mode of Chrome. Do as follows: <ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li ">Open Incognito window</li><li class="- topic/li ">Go to <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">chrome://extensions</codeph></li><li class="- topic/li ">Find the Katalon Studio extension, click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Details</uicontrol></li><li class="- topic/li ">Toggle the button <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Allow in Incognito</uicontrol></li></ul></p></li></ol></conbody></concept>